Scope
-----
This record preserves the v1.8 Safety Firewall evidence harness results for the Trusted Friend Biped Poppy handoff. The firewall is a Layer 2 evidence harness. It does not replace the ESP32 Layer 1 ROM authority; it proves that unsafe command proposals are denied or routed to LIMP_SHUTDOWN before live hardware commands proceed.

